gg_bkh_majestic_v3

This map is a second release that has been modified with the following.
  • Added a new skybow
  • Totally restructured the outer walls
  • Eliminated the landmines
  • Eliminated the tunnel
  • Rebuilt the bridge in the center
  • Upgraded lighting

    Map Features

  • Circular and arched brushes
  • A cannon that shoots barrels on top of each spawn castle.
  • 8 rope ladders
  • 20 Spawnpoints

    Special Thanks

  • A special thanks to Rumpelbude for the excellent work on the skybox.

Open to all constructive criticism.
